{"tid":2055821,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[中伏] 口罩工廠 Mask Factory","createTime":"2020-06-08T08:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-10T11:33:02.000Z","uid":45607,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6d467ba7df1f12f56e65273d20091e2bb21529","tid":2055821,"uid":45607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:46:18.000Z","msg":"呢間野有晒前科<br />\n假證書 ： <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2018868/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2018868/page/1?post=2</a><br />\n口罩唔合格：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1923148/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1923148/page/1</a><br />\n老闆為人唔老實：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1896058/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1896058/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地係流浮山小紅書倉個邊個無塵間其實係做樣，員工出入唔洗消毒，唔洗戴口罩，口罩材料亂擺亂放。口罩最重要中間個層物料勁污糟，同抹地布差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n最近收到風佢地係元朗開左間廠做過濾層，但質素係點大家心知肚明。<br />\n買左既敢唔敢用大家決定。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763ed482c83e716ee346ffd64ad91c92dfb8248f","tid":2055821,"uid":45607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"Ｄ機大部份都係大陸黎，製成品係點大家都明。"},{"pid":"0cb37e16c5c15e98e6a5308a969813e232c36a11","tid":2055821,"uid":265943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"唔係化，後日去取貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e46196047e9bd9984580edd67415040bd01482","tid":2055821,"uid":45607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cb37e16c5c15e98e6a5308a969813e232c36a11","tid":2055821,"uid":265943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:17:15.000Z","msg":"唔係化，後日去取貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T09:43:31.000Z","msg":"退錢保平安"},{"pid":"86b61eb80fb259753c3fd06f2e790be1bb0ff2cb","tid":2055821,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu